<div class="page-width" style="padding: 4rem 1rem; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff;">
  <h2 style="font-size: 1.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 2rem;">FAQ</h2>
  
  <div class="product-faq-container">
    <details class="p-faq-item">
      <summary class="p-faq-summary">
        <span class="p-faq-icon">+</span>
        <span class="p-faq-question">What Are Embroidered Patches?</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-faq-answer">
        Embroidered patches are decorative pieces of fabric featuring designs created by stitching colored threads onto a base material.
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="p-faq-item">
      <summary class="p-faq-summary">
        <span class="p-faq-icon">+</span>
        <span class="p-faq-question">How Are Embroidered Patches Made?</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-faq-answer">
        Embroidered patches are made using computerized embroidery machines that stitch intricate designs onto a fabric backing.
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="p-faq-item">
      <summary class="p-faq-summary">
        <span class="p-faq-icon">+</span>
        <span class="p-faq-question">What Are The Applications Of Embroidered Patches?</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-faq-answer">
        Used across many industries including military, law enforcement, corporate branding, sports teams, etc.
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="p-faq-item">
      <summary class="p-faq-summary">
        <span class="p-faq-icon">+</span>
        <span class="p-faq-question">Why Choose Embroidered Patches?</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-faq-answer">
        Durability, professional appearance, and versatility. Withstand repeated washing and provide a classic textured look.
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="p-faq-item">
      <summary class="p-faq-summary">
        <span class="p-faq-icon">+</span>
        <span class="p-faq-question">How To Attach Embroidered Patches</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-faq-answer">
        Iron-on, sew-on, velcro backing, or adhesive backing. Heat-press application is our most popular method.
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="p-faq-item">
      <summary class="p-faq-summary">
        <span class="p-faq-icon">+</span>
        <span class="p-faq-question">What Types Of Embroidered Patches Do You Offer?</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-faq-answer">
        Standard embroidered, 3D puff, metallic thread, glow-in-the-dark, and more.
      </div>
    </details>

     <details class="p-faq-item">
      <summary class="p-faq-summary">
        <span class="p-faq-icon">+</span>
        <span class="p-faq-question">What Makes Embroidered Patches Different?</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-faq-answer">
        Textured, dimensional appearance created by actual thread stitching. Premium look and feel compared to printed.
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
  
